{"word":"G2156 - εὐσχημόνως - euschēmónōs - yoo-skhay-mon'-ose - Decently","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐσχημόνως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">euschēmónōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-skhay-mon'-ose</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Decently</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீராய், நல்லொழுக்கமாய், யோக்கியமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"in a seemly manner, decently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G2158 - εὐσχήμων - euschḗmōn - yoo-skhay'-mone/2158\">G2158</a>; <i>decorously:</i> - decently, honestly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}